\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Feedback linearization and input-output decoupling of a quadrotor using
 dynamic extension.
 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

 denote snap, jerk, acceleration and velocity respectively.
 Based on 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "mistler2001exact"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "fig:feedback_lin"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

